               <p>The case was stated by Mr. Alley.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18120115-71-person758">
                  JOHN 
                  FLETCHER WILKINSON
               <interp inst="t18120115-71-person758" type="surname" value="FLETCHER WILKINSON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18120115-71-person758" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
